{"tid":783524,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=?? 【新昌財困】員工狂呻：7月份糧都未出 好多人要供樓架","createTime":"2018-08-17T15:05:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-28T08:56:43.000Z","uid":19454,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"82aa5f587bd87bf40cd2196f5059c139322f809d","tid":783524,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T15:05:24.000Z","msg":"西九文化區內的「M+博物館」總承建商新昌（404），因陷入資金困難，更有員工及判頭指新昌欠薪，而西九管理局今日更公佈，正式終止與新昌的工程合約。<br />\n<br />\n近日有員工聲稱至今仍未收到7月份工資，是近年來首次。有員工並爆料指公司以支票替公司車輛續牌時，遭到彈票，而金額只是1萬元。<br />\n新昌員工最新向本報指，7月的薪金，至今日止仍未發放，同事有向人事部追薪，但至今未有作任何交代，「同事啲脾氣都唔係好架啦，糧又冇出，<span style=\"color: red;\">好多人要供樓要養家</span>，大家都好Desperate，總之就係士氣低落。」至於「M+博物館」被解約，該員工指，自己只是比西九管理局官方公佈前10分鐘才知道。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180817/58576750\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180817%2F58576750&d=HznOOnqaT1YeGSJD2gOPpZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=a886e513\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180817%2F58576750&h=c12a5d85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180817/58576750</a>"},{"pid":"ab35911ac827f9f79b2000c274aaac141b3e2e5b","tid":783524,"uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T15:06:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/12/164607_750ddbf3ac6d9374f8e9193aa94ad2a7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F12%2F164607_750ddbf